  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK934">
<l>ciṟumai palaceytu cīraḻikkuñ cūtiṉ </l>
<l> vaṟumai taruvatoṉ ṟil</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>There is nothing else that brings (us) poverty like gambling which causes many a misery and destroys (one's) reputation.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
